vessel-caracara-name = МИ-КОР Caracara
vessel-caracara-desc = A Militia Ironworks salvage frigate fitted with an Apollo super‑mining laser. Its forward cockpit offers a clear view of the dig site. Includes an  ultra‑efficient pinch reactor, basic FTL, and a compact galley for long shifts in the belt. When paired with the Apollo, its three 20 mm mounts provide adequate defensive fire.
